#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/_includes/smallrye-kafka-incoming.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When `partitions` is greater than 1, this attribute allows configuring how many records are requested by each consumer every time.\n"
"\n"
"Type: _int_"
msgstr "Quando o valor de `“partitions”` for maior que 1, este atributo permite configurar quantos registros são solicitados por cada consumidor a cada vez."

